regen.absent_element: situation when a user without necessary privileges attempts global renumbering
regen.new_specification: The system shall deny global renumbering of bridge keys if the user lacks necessary privileges and notify the user of insufficient access rights.

regen.absent_element: user privilege conditions for global renumbering of bridge keys
regen.new_specification: The system shall restrict global renumbering of bridge keys to users with the appropriate privilege level, verified through user authentication.

regen.absent_element: user privilege check on creating, editing, or removing structures
regen.new_specification: The system shall verify user privileges before allowing the creation, editing, or removal of structures.

label: The renumbering shall be restricted depending on the user privilege
absence: The renumbering function shall be restricted depending on the user privilege
